{"issuance_frequency":"","notes_translated":{"fr":"Au travail comme à la maison, de nombreux dispositifs utilisent la technologie Bluetooth (portables, imprimantes, récepteurs GPS, téléphones, moniteurs d’activité physique, appareils ménagers, systèmes audio de voitures). Or, des auteurs de menace peuvent se servir de vulnérabilités du Bluetooth pour exploiter vos dispositifs et voler votre information. Bien que cette technologie soit un moyen efficace et peu coûteux de connecter vos dispositifs, il convient de l’utiliser avec vigilance.\r\n","en":"Many business and personal devices (e.g. laptops, printers, GPS receivers, phones, fitness trackers, home appliances, and car audio systems) use Bluetooth technology. However, threat actors can use Bluetooth-specific vulnerabilities to exploit your devices to steal your information. Bluetooth technology is a low-cost and effective way to connect your devices, but should be used with caution.\r\n"},"issn":"","imso_approval":"true","isbn":"","creator":"","org_section":{"fr":"Centre canadien pour la cybersécurité (CCC)","en":"Canadian Centre for Cyber Security (CCCS)"},"jurisdiction":"federal","private":false,"maintainer_email":"open-ouvert@tbs-sct.gc.ca","num_tags":0,"edition":"","frequency":"not_planned","data_series_issue_identification":{"fr":"","en":""},"contributor":{"fr":"","en":""},"maintainer":null,"ready_to_publish":"true","id":"71c91d55-94e7-4753-a4da-b5919d93f20c","metadata_created":"2019-12-12T21:28:28.994801","subject":["information_and_communications","science_and_technology"],"pspc_identification_number":"","metadata_modified":"2019-12-12T21:28:28.994808","author":null,"author_email":null,"geographic_region":[],"portal_release_date":"2019-12-12","digital_object_identifier":"","state":"active","version":null,"keywords":{"fr":["Cyberdéfense","Mobilité","Accès à distance","Sans fil","Gestion des risques"],"en":["Cyber Defence","Mobility","Remote Access","Wireless","Risk Management","Travel"]},"relationships_as_o